Ledell LEE, et al., petitioners,
v.
Asa HUTCHINSON, Governor of Arkansas, et al.
No. 16-8788 (16A1012).
Supreme Court of the United States
April 20, 2017.
Application for stay of execution of sentences of death presented to Justice ALITO and by him referred to the Court denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eighth Circuit denied.
